data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom home centrally located to shopping, restaurants, and more! Minutes from historic downtown Summerville and I-26! Home offers 4 massive size bedrooms, 2.5 baths, over 3,506 sq. ft. of living space, hardwood floors on the first level, gas burning fire place, and more! The entrance way features high ceilings with additional 2nd story windows providing tons of extra natural light! This area offers a formal sitting area with a gas burning fire place and is perfect for entertaining friends and family. The separate formal dining room offers crown molding and a large eating area. The first floor also offers an optional room for an office or separate game room for the kids. To the back of the home is an additional living room area open to the kitchen.
